- whether_is_abnormal_metric(container.net.tcp.retransmits) and container.net.if_dropped/if_errors (for packet loss/retransmits);
- whether_is_abnormal_metric(container.net.rtt or synthetic ping) (for network latency);
- whether_is_abnormal_metric(container.cpu.usage) and container.process.cpu (for CPU overload);
- collect_trace on the frontend→checkoutservice gRPC calls to see where time is spent (network vs server CPU).
